{"tid":1019837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子apm中庭墮樓 昏迷送院不治","createTime":"2019-02-13T08:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T12:20:38.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c5de74e8c5c0015ba931f8ef632255227fce5d","tid":1019837,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"中午1時半，觀塘apm一名男子，由商場內中庭高處墮下，倒卧大堂地面，重創昏迷，保安員報警求助，並將男子倒卧位置以板圍封。救護員到場為事主進行心外壓急救，惟送院後證實不治，警方調查後獲悉男子姓錢（73歲），據悉他有身體病患，事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n讀者Alex當時剛吃完飯，在商場行街，突聽到有人大叫：「有人跳樓呀！」他即走出查看，已見一名男子倒卧地上，昏迷不醒。<br />\n<br />\n警員在商場5樓發現一支拐杖，相信為錢伯所有，同時估計該處為錢伯墮樓位置。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiYcyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=3a84e483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190213/59254298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190213%2F59254298&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiYcyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=560b85f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190213%2F59254298&h=1a74d968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190213/59254298</a>"},{"pid":"dfeb5657122316e16dbf5e2c2b6a8427a8240549","tid":1019837,"uid":62822,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:03:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"295bc7469e2eb4a19a7c4611f63c123a49493302","tid":1019837,"uid":50740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"唔要4000?